trans-unit.source: Provides a strongly typed <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceView"></xref> object for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Fornece um com tipo seguro <xref href="System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceView"> </xref> do objeto para o <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource"> </xref> controlo.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource> control enables ASP.NET data-bound controls, such as the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> controls, to bind to site map data.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource>controlo permite controlos do ASP.NET vinculados a dados, tais como o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controlos, para vincular a dados de mapa de site.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TreeView> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource>

trans-unit.source: The SiteMapDataSourceView class is used by controls developers but it is not used by page developers nor in page code.
trans-unit.target: A classe de SiteMapDataSourceView é utilizada pelos programadores de controlos, mas não é utilizado pelos programadores página nem no código da página.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource> returns a SiteMapDataSourceView for a specified hierarchical path when the <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceView.Select%2A> method is called.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource>devolve um SiteMapDataSourceView para um caminho de hierárquico especificado quando o <xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceView.Select%2A>método é chamado.</xref:System.Web.UI.HierarchicalDataSourceView.Select%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource>

trans-unit.source: Like all hierarchical data source view objects, the SiteMapDataSourceView is not named; rather, its is identified by its unique hierarchical path.
trans-unit.target: Como todos os objetos de vista hierárquica de dados de origem a SiteMapDataSourceView não tem um nome; em vez disso, o é identificado pelo caminho dela hierárquico exclusivo.

trans-unit.source: The SiteMapDataSourceView is a wrapper class on a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> collection.
trans-unit.target: O SiteMapDataSourceView é uma classe de wrapper num <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>coleção.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> class implements the <xref:System.Web.UI.IHierarchicalEnumerable> interface, which the SiteMapDataSourceView class returns from a call to `Select` method.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>classe implementa o <xref:System.Web.UI.IHierarchicalEnumerable>interface, o que devolve a partir de uma chamada para a classe de SiteMapDataSourceView `Select` método.</xref:System.Web.UI.IHierarchicalEnumerable> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>

trans-unit.source: Because the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource> and SiteMapDataSourceView work with <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode> objects, the view maintains an internal <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> to contain them.
trans-unit.target: Porque o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource>e SiteMapDataSourceView funcionam com <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode>objetos, a vista mantém um interno <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>para contê-los.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> </xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSource>

trans-unit.source: The collection is initialized using the view's constructors and accessed with the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView.Select%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: A coleção foi inicializada com construtores da vista e acedidos com o <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView.Select%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView.Select%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new named instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView"></xref> class, adding the single specified node to the internal collection of nodes.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova com o nome de instância do <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView"> </xref> classe, adicionar único nó especificado para a coleção de nós interna.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView> class is a wrapper class on a <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView>classe é uma classe de wrapper num <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection>objeto.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapNodeCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView>

trans-unit.source: Creating a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView> using the SiteMapDataSourceView constructor initializes the internal node collection with a single <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode> object.
trans-unit.target: Criar um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView>utilizar o construtor de SiteMapDataSourceView inicializa a coleção do nó interna com um único <xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode>objeto.</xref:System.Web.SiteMapNode> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView>

trans-unit.source: The site map structure is navigated using the node as a point of reference.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView> class implements the inherited ExecuteSelect method to retrieve a set of nodes that represents the site navigation structure for the current ASP.NET application.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView>classe implementa o método ExecuteSelect herdado para obter um conjunto de nós que representa a estrutura de navegação do site para a aplicação ASP.NET atual.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView>

trans-unit.source: Page developers and data-bound control authors do not call the ExecuteSelect method directly; instead, use the publicly exposed <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView.Select%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Os programadores de página e autores de controlo vinculado a dados não chamam o método ExecuteSelect diretamente; em alternativa, utilize publicamente expostas <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView.Select%2A>método.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SiteMapDataSourceView.Select%2A>
